                "ADULT",
                "OLDER_ADULT"
            ],
            "studyPopulation": "The study population consists of men and / or women over 18 years of age, with no upper limit age, with histologically confirmed non-metastatic rectal adenocarcinoma and for whom treatment with nRCT has been indicated.",
